      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=vyoqz53k1x]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vyoqz53k1x]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ag70gubhf5]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ag70gubhf5]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ag70gubhf5\">Project</span></strong>: Kaboom Box</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"vyoqz53k1x\">HDA </span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/hopeschroers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hope Schroers</a></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/kaboom-box/kaboom_box.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627477935&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611647560/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627477935&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611647589\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611647560\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"5afd44ea-77cc-4218-9775-aba87662349f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627477935&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627477935&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h2 id=\"KaboomBox-Overview\">Overview</h2><p>This Houdini Digital Asset will greatly speed up pyro and volume workflows by giving artists a toolkit to render explosions, fire, candles, and anything else in between. The HDA offers both basic and advanced pyro lookdev controls plus a few presets to get you going quickly and easily.</p><p>Developed at Pixar by FX TD Hope Schroers, this HDA is a robust shading network developed using native RenderMan nodes and the best practices for rendering volumes at Pixar Animation Studios.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627552543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611647560/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627552543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611319921\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611647560\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3aa26320-7234-4f92-8ca7-19991d22e55d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627552543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627552543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"KaboomBox-Installation\">Installation</h2><p>This Pyro HDA is simple to install:</p><ul><li><p>Download the Kaboom Box HDA</p></li><li><p>Open Houdini&rsquo;s Asset Menu</p></li><li><p>Choose Install Asset Library</p></li><li><p>Select rman_kaboom_box.hda</p></li><li><p>Press install</p></li></ul><p>For more in depth information about using The Kaboom Box, please visit the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki.pixar.com/display/RFH/Kaboom+Box+HDA\" rel=\"nofollow\">RenderMan documentation</a>.</p><hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"KaboomBox-AbouttheArtist\">About the Artist</h3><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/hopeschroers\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"hope-schroers-headshot.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/hope-schroers-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627614937&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611647560/hope-schroers-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627614937&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611287153\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"hope-schroers-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611647560\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"38ae99ce-e306-4a6c-bcb3-fde83ca1f3de\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/hope-schroers-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627614937&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611647560/hope-schroers-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627614937&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\" /></span></a><p>Hope Schroers is an FX technical director who&rsquo;s worked at Pixar on films such as <em>Elemental</em>, <em>Lightyear</em>, and <em>Luca</em>. She loves merging her technical skills with her passion for photography and illustration.</p><hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a1fa7e7c-4e76-4717-ac93-bd2e12953610\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"KaboomBox-Attribution-NonCommercial4.0International(CCBY-NC4.0)\">Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)</h3></div></div><p /><p /><p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
